1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if your heartbeat is telling you more than you think?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:08,800
An ECG, or electrocardiogram, captures the electrical activity of your heart.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:10,800
But why is this important?

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:13,600
Your heart's rhythm can reveal hidden issues.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:17,600
For instance, irregularities can indicate arrhythmias or even heart attacks.

6
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:21,600
Understanding ECGs empowers you to take charge of your health.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,600
Curious about your heart’s health?

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,000
Explore ECGs further and stay informed!
